getGhostAttributes(uint256).author: @ziweidream

params._id: the node id of the ghost

getGhostAttributes(uint256).return: its kittyID, its original owner, whether it is a replacement kittie,        the loser kitty for which it is a replacement kittie(0 if this ghost is a loser kittie itself)

getGhostIdForKittie(uint256).author: @ziweidream
getGhostIdForKittie(uint256).return: node id of the kittie (if the kittie is not a ghost, it returns 0)

getLastGhostId().author: @ziweidream
getLastGhostId().return: the node id of the last node

getNumberOfSacrificeKitties(uint256).author: @ziweidream

params._kittieID: the kittieID of the loser kittie

getNumberOfSacrificeKitties(uint256).return: the number of sacrificing kitties already in HELL for this loser kittie

getTotalKTYsLockedInKittieHell().return: the total amount of KTYs locked in kittieHELL contract

getTotalNumberOfGhostsInHell().author: @ziweidream
getTotalNumberOfGhostsInHell().return: the total number of kittie ghosts permanently locked in HELL

isKittieGhost(uint256).author: @ziweidream
isKittieGhost(uint256).return: true if the kittie is a permanent ghost, false if the kittie is not permanently dead

lockKTYsInKittieHell(uint256,uint256).details: This function can only be carried out via kittieHELL contractrecord the KTY amount locked in kittieHELL contract

params._kittieID: the kittieID of the loser kittie who lost a game
params._kty_amount: the redemption fee locked in kittieHELL contract                   for redeeming the loser kittie

loserKittieToHell(uint256,address).details: This function can only be carried out via kittieHELL contractAdd the node _id of a loser kittie to GhostsList

params._kittieID: the kittieID of the loser kittie who lost a game
params._owner: the owner of the loser kittie

sacrificeKittieToHell(uint256,address,ui.author: @ziweidream
sacrificeKittieToHell(uint256,address,ui.details: This function can only be carried out via proxyAdd the node _id of a sacrificing kittie to GhostsList

params._kittieID: the kittieID of the loser kittie who lost a game
params._owner: the owner of the loser kittie
params._sacrificeKittie: the kittieID of the sacrificing kittie for redeeming the loser kittie
